text: Jambole is a settlement in Kenya's Kwale County. It is also the name of a dance craze made popular by the 2014 song and YouTube video "Sitya Loss" by Ugandan Eddie Kenzo. Kenya and Uganda are partners in the East African Community (EAC) and Swahili as a common language shared among many. == References == Category:Populated places in Coast Province Category:Kwale County
title: Jambole
